**AI Overview**

**+16**

Yes, there are many AI tools for legal questions, ranging from free chatbots for basic information to powerful, specialized assistants for legal professionals that assist with research, drafting, and analysis. Examples for professionals include Harvey, Lexis+ AI, and Westlaw Precision, while some tools like LawConnect offer free AI chat for straightforward legal information.

**AI for legal professionals**

[**Harvey:**](https://www.google.com/search?client=safari&sca_esv=d1a2c1eff646079b&hl=en-us&q=Harvey&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwikx8_m29mQAxV4mGoFHW2pD8EQxccNegUIuwEQAw&mstk=AUtExfD-QNin4vywr_RSETgn7roalX1b1HERWbn52_wH0CvjLuH1JXndbhpVnGIFTPIMVff16tNzcbmVVBFWQN9iujyp38NnRBF2SB-FVkBCw12kb6Zh4vqvq0tuyULEpWXNWls&csui=3) A legal AI assistant that helps with research, drafting, and other complex tasks by providing grounded results with accurate citations.

[**Lexis+ AI](https://www.google.com/search?client=safari&sca_esv=d1a2c1eff646079b&hl=en-us&q=Lexis%2B+AI&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwikx8_m29mQAxV4mGoFHW2pD8EQxccNegUIvQEQAQ&mstk=AUtExfD-QNin4vywr_RSETgn7roalX1b1HERWbn52_wH0CvjLuH1JXndbhpVnGIFTPIMVff16tNzcbmVVBFWQN9iujyp38NnRBF2SB-FVkBCw12kb6Zh4vqvq0tuyULEpWXNWls&csui=3):** A comprehensive legal AI solution from LexisNexis for research, drafting, and analysis.

[**Westlaw Precision](https://www.google.com/search?client=safari&sca_esv=d1a2c1eff646079b&hl=en-us&q=Westlaw+Precision&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwikx8_m29mQAxV4mGoFHW2pD8EQxccNegUIvwEQAQ&mstk=AUtExfD-QNin4vywr_RSETgn7roalX1b1HERWbn52_wH0CvjLuH1JXndbhpVnGIFTPIMVff16tNzcbmVVBFWQN9iujyp38NnRBF2SB-FVkBCw12kb6Zh4vqvq0tuyULEpWXNWls&csui=3):** An AI-powered legal research tool developed by Thomson Reuters.

[**CoCounsel Legal](https://www.google.com/search?client=safari&sca_esv=d1a2c1eff646079b&hl=en-us&q=CoCounsel+Legal&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwikx8_m29mQAxV4mGoFHW2pD8EQxccNegUI1gEQAQ&mstk=AUtExfD-QNin4vywr_RSETgn7roalX1b1HERWbn52_wH0CvjLuH1JXndbhpVnGIFTPIMVff16tNzcbmVVBFWQN9iujyp38NnRBF2SB-FVkBCw12kb6Zh4vqvq0tuyULEpWXNWls&csui=3):** An AI assistant from Thomson Reuters that helps with research, document analysis, and drafting.

[**Paxton AI](https://www.google.com/search?client=safari&sca_esv=d1a2c1eff646079b&hl=en-us&q=Paxton+AI&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwikx8_m29mQAxV4mGoFHW2pD8EQxccNegUI1wEQAQ&mstk=AUtExfD-QNin4vywr_RSETgn7roalX1b1HERWbn52_wH0CvjLuH1JXndbhpVnGIFTPIMVff16tNzcbmVVBFWQN9iujyp38NnRBF2SB-FVkBCw12kb6Zh4vqvq0tuyULEpWXNWls&csui=3):** An AI assistant for legal professionals that helps with research, drafting motions, and summarizing documents.

[**Winnow AI](https://www.google.com/search?client=safari&sca_esv=d1a2c1eff646079b&hl=en-us&q=Winnow+AI&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwikx8_m29mQAxV4mGoFHW2pD8EQxccNegUI3QEQAQ&mstk=AUtExfD-QNin4vywr_RSETgn7roalX1b1HERWbn52_wH0CvjLuH1JXndbhpVnGIFTPIMVff16tNzcbmVVBFWQN9iujyp38NnRBF2SB-FVkBCw12kb6Zh4vqvq0tuyULEpWXNWls&csui=3):** A legal research assistant that uses AI to answer basic legal questions based on a database of attorney-reviewed content.

**AI for general legal information**

[**LawConnect](https://www.google.com/search?client=safari&sca_esv=d1a2c1eff646079b&hl=en-us&q=LawConnect&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwikx8_m29mQAxV4mGoFHW2pD8EQxccNegUImQEQAQ&mstk=AUtExfD-QNin4vywr_RSETgn7roalX1b1HERWbn52_wH0CvjLuH1JXndbhpVnGIFTPIMVff16tNzcbmVVBFWQN9iujyp38NnRBF2SB-FVkBCw12kb6Zh4vqvq0tuyULEpWXNWls&csui=3):** A free AI chat that provides straightforward legal information on topics like contracts and consumer rights.

**Other AI tools**

